author: bibryam
msg: Added ajax autocompleter support to lookup screens in accounting, party, product and workeffort components.
Also added possibility for passing additional condition to search query. This can be seen in party lookup screens, used to filter disabled parties.
Specifying return field is not required any more - the first field from search fields is used as return field.
